You must build the SDK with Java Wrapping enabled to run this.

Build and run this with the swig classes in your classpath and the
libs on your library paths.  For example,

javac -classpath .:../capi/src/build/swig *.java
DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=../capi/src/build/swig java -classpath .:../capi/src/build/swig Testing


Windows Example:
 - copy JavaVisTrails.dll and VisTrails.dll into this directory
 - javac -cp .;..\build\capi\src\swig *.java
 - java -cp .;..\build\capi\src\swig Testing